snippet.title: The Respondent w Attorney Todd Lander
snippet.description:
Join Todd Lander, Esq. today at 1pm PT for a special livestream Q&A to discuss Amber Heard's upcoming defamation trial. Johnny Depp contends he was wrongly/falsely accused of domestic abuse by Heard and is requesting $50 million in damages in a complaint filed in March 2019, set to be 'heard' on May 21, 2021 in Virginia.

Todd Lander is a partner at the Century City law firm Freeman, Freeman & Smiley and Chair of the Litigation Department. He specializes in shareholder disputes and intellectual property matters.
